pulses.name: 20240827 Most Active Threat Indicators
pulses.description:
27 Aug 2024 : Most Active Threat Indicators
#Cybersecurity #Cyberattack #RCE #Botnet #IOC

Top 3 Source Countries:

- China (CN): Responsible for multiple attacks, including botnets, remote code execution vulnerabilities in various devices like Mozi, Netgear, D-Link, and Dasan GPON routers.
- India (IN): Involved in several attacks exploiting remote command injection vulnerabilities in GPON routers, as well as web shells and remote code execution in D-Link devices.
- United States (US): Observed in attacks using Nmap script scanners, web application vulnerabilities like Apache HTTP Server cgi-bin path traversal, and backdoors like AndroxGh0st malware.
